 <p>

<tr><td colspan=2>
<p><hr><p>
I am a member of the <a href="http://www.cs.bham.ac.uk/research/groupings/theory/">Birmingham Theoretical Computer Science group</a>, and my interests include 
<ul>
<li> semantics of programming languages, including denotational, operational and game semantics
<li> computational effects, both individually and generally
<li> call-by-push-value
<li> semantics of nondeterminism
<li> category theory, in particular categorical semantics and coalgebra.
</ul>
If you're interested in PhD research in any of the above topics, please <a href="mailto:P.B.Levy@cs.bham.ac.uk">contact me</a>. <p>

<p><hr><p>
</td>
</table>


